<%- include('../partials/header') %>

<!-- ============ HERO ============ -->
<section class="lp-hero">
  <div class="inner">
    <div>
      <div class="eyebrow">Yoga — the refined way of life</div>
      <h1>Learn yoga the way it was meant to be taught — from a Guru, never sold.</h1>
      <p class="sub">Yogasamskruthi carries forward the teaching of Yoga Guru Narasimhamurthy: asana, pranayama, meditation, ayurveda and time in nature — shared as a service, one aspirant at a time.</p>
      <div class="row">
        <% if (!me) { %>
          <a class="btn lp" href="/join">Begin your practice — free</a>
          <a class="btn lp-ghost" href="/teach">Teach as a Guruji</a>
        <% } else { %>
          <a class="btn lp" href="/<%= me.role %>">Go to my dashboard</a>
          <a class="btn lp-ghost" href="/learn/yogaasana">Explore the teachings</a>
        <% } %>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-note">No fees. Register with your intention and a Guruji will guide you.</div>
    </div>
    <%- include('../partials/mandala') %>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============ TRUST BAR ============ -->
<div class="trustbar">
  <div class="t"><b>25,000+</b><span>students taught in our lineage</span></div>
  <div class="t"><b>1988</b><span>practising since</span></div>
  <div class="t"><b><%= gurus.length %></b><span>verified Gurujis</span></div>
  <div class="t"><b>Never sold</b><span>yoga taught as service</span></div>
</div>

<!-- ============ WHAT WE TEACH ============ -->
<div class="center">
  <div class="sec-h">What we teach</div>
  <p class="intro">The complete practice — not postures alone, but the whole refined way of living.</p>
</div>
<div class="offer">
  <% const glyphs = {yogaasana:'आ', pranayama:'प्र', dhyanam:'ध्या', 'mudra-vignanam':'मु', trekking:'गि', ayurveda:'आयु', blogs:'ले', pravachanas:'प्र', 'advisory-services':'से', gallery:'चि'}; %>
  <% const blurbs = {
      yogaasana:'Postures that bring steadiness, health and lightness of limb.',
      pranayama:'Working with the breath to expand and steady the life force.',
      dhyanam:'Meditation — the deeper stillness the practice leads toward.',
      'mudra-vignanam':'The science of gestures that direct energy within.',
      trekking:'Prakruthi pravaasa — journeying through nature as practice.',
      ayurveda:'Everyday guidance on food, habits and healing.',
      blogs:'Writings and reflections from our teachers.',
      pravachanas:'Discourses and spiritual talks.',
      'advisory-services':'Guidance offered to aspirants and the community.',
      gallery:'Moments from practice, treks and gatherings.'
    }; %>
  <% (navPages||[]).forEach(p => { %>
    <a href="/learn/<%= p.slug %>">
      <div class="glyph"><%= glyphs[p.slug] || 'ॐ' %></div>
      <h3><%= p.title %></h3>
      <p><%= blurbs[p.slug] || 'Explore this practice.' %></p>
    </a>
  <% }) %>
</div>

<!-- ============ LINEAGE ============ -->
<div class="center"><div class="sec-h">The Guru we follow</div></div>
<div class="lineage">
  <div class="portrait">
    <div>
      <div class="om">ॐ</div>
      <b>Yoga Guru Narasimhamurthy</b>
      <small>1934 – 2016</small>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div>
    <h3 style="margin-top:0">A realised yogi who gave yoga away</h3>
    <p class="muted">Sri A. S. Narasimha Murthy Guruji lived a family life, yet through penance attained a very high position in Astanga yoga. He carried the blessings of Lord Shiva and was trained by veteran Himalayan yogis. He gained many siddhis but seldom exhibited them, living a simple and innocent life.</p>
    <p class="muted">He never sold yoga — he considered teaching it a service to the Almighty, and guided more than 25,000 students across India under Acharya Sri Adi Shankara Yoga Kendra, helping them with their physical, mental and spiritual well-being.</p>
    <p class="muted">This platform exists to preserve his teachings and walk the path he directed.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ============ TEACHERS ============ -->
<div class="center">
  <div class="sec-h">Our Gurujis</div>
  <p class="intro">Every teacher here is verified before they can accept an aspirant. Choose the one whose path matches your intention.</p>
</div>
<div class="teachers">
  <% gurus.forEach(g => { %>
    <div class="tcard">
      <div class="avatar"><%= g.name.replace(/^Guruji\s+/,'').split(' ').map(w=>w[0]).slice(0,2).join('') %></div>
      <h3><%= g.name %></h3>
      <span class="pill <%= g.expertise %>"><%= g.expertise %></span>
      <p><%= (g.bio||'').slice(0,150) %><%= (g.bio||'').length>150?'…':'' %></p>
      <a class="btn ghost sm" href="/gurujis/<%= g.id %>">View profile</a>
    </div>
  <% }) %>
  <% if(!gurus.length){ %><div class="empty">Gurujis will appear here once verified.</div><% } %>
</div>

<!-- ============ HOW IT WORKS ============ -->
<div class="center" style="margin-top:34px">
  <div class="sec-h">How to begin</div>
  <p class="intro">Three steps from curiosity to guided practice.</p>
</div>
<div class="steps">
  <div class="st"><b>1</b><h3>Register your intention</h3><p>Create a free account and say what you wish to learn and by when. Your intention is what a Guruji reads first.</p></div>
  <div class="st"><b>2</b><h3>Apply to a Guruji</h3><p>Read the teachers' profiles and writings, then apply to the one who fits your path. They accept or respond with guidance.</p></div>
  <div class="st"><b>3</b><h3>Learn and practise</h3><p>Once accepted, ask questions any time and meet your Guruji in scheduled audio or video sessions.</p></div>
</div>
<div class="center" style="margin-top:20px">
  <% if(!me){ %><a class="btn lp" href="/join" style="background:var(--green);color:#fff">Create your free account</a><% } %>
</div>

<!-- ============ WHY ============ -->
<div class="center" style="margin-top:36px">
  <div class="sec-h">Why Yogasamskruthi</div>
  <p class="intro">We are a community carrying a tradition, not a subscription service.</p>
</div>
<div class="why">
  <div class="w"><b>Taught as a service</b><span>Following our Guru's example, yoga here is never sold. Teachers give their time to the community.</span></div>
  <div class="w"><b>A real Guru, not a video</b><span>You apply to a specific teacher who reads your intention and guides you personally over live sessions.</span></div>
  <div class="w"><b>Every teacher verified</b><span>Gurujis submit their background for verification and are approved by the admin before teaching.</span></div>
  <div class="w"><b>The whole tradition</b><span>Asana, pranayama, dhyana, mudra, ayurveda and trekking — the complete way of life, not fitness alone.</span></div>
</div>

<!-- ============ FAQ ============ -->
<div class="center" style="margin-top:36px">
  <div class="sec-h">Common questions</div>
</div>
<div class="faq">
  <details><summary>Is there any fee to learn here?</summary><p>No. Following our Guru's example, yoga is taught here as a service rather than sold. You register, state your intention, and a Guruji guides you.</p></details>
  <details><summary>I am a complete beginner. Can I still join?</summary><p>Yes. Say so honestly in your intention when you register — your Guruji will start you where you are, with the breath and the basics before anything demanding.</p></details>
  <details><summary>How do the sessions actually happen?</summary><p>Once a Guruji accepts your application, either of you can schedule a session. A private audio/video meeting link is generated automatically for the time you agree on.</p></details>
  <details><summary>How do I become a Guruji here?</summary><p>Register through “Teach as a Guruji” and submit any relevant document. Background verification is done by the admin team before your account is enabled — you can sign in once approved.</p></details>
  <details><summary>Can I ask questions between sessions?</summary><p>Yes. Once you are accepted by a Guruji, you can send questions any time from your dashboard, and their answers appear there.</p></details>
  <details><summary>Is the Ayurveda guidance medical advice?</summary><p>No. It is traditional guidance shared with our community by Yoga Vismaya Trust. Please follow it at your own discretion and consult a qualified practitioner for medical concerns.</p></details>
</div>

<!-- ============ CLOSING CTA ============ -->
<div class="closing">
  <h2>Begin where you are</h2>
  <p>Celebrate the practice and experience the bliss in every moment. Register your intention and let a Guruji guide the rest.</p>
  <div class="row" style="justify-content:center">
    <% if(!me){ %>
      <a class="btn lp" href="/join">Join as an aspirant</a>
      <a class="btn lp-ghost" href="/login">Sign in</a>
    <% } else { %>
      <a class="btn lp" href="/<%= me.role %>">Go to my dashboard</a>
    <% } %>
  </div>
</div>

<%- include('../partials/footer') %>
